			<div style="padding-left:30px;">
				<pre>组件已经为hasClass("widget-slide")的节点自动添加slide效果，默认参数有：
	{
		tabSelector : '.slide-nav li',
		viewSelector : '.slide-content li',
		pageUpSelector: '.slide-pageup',
		pageDownSelector: '.slide-pagedown',
		autoPlay: true,
		supportMouseenter: true,
		mouseenterSwitchTime: 300
	}
也可以通过设置元素的jss来修改或添加slide参数，如以下:
&lt;div class="picslide widget-slide" data-jss="autoPlayTime:1000,animType:'scroll'" &gt;</pre>
